item.title: About
item.description: Hi, I’m ChiLin Chiu. You can call me ChiLin. ^^ I’m a senior AI software engineer. Building AI service and products from scratch, including data collect, data clearning, model building, system design and development, and deployment. Mainly focus on Smart Factory domain. Familar with Python, learning Rust. Believe software change the world and bring convenience to life. Fans of Elon Musk, work hard like hell, spend more 3500 hours on work.
